Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹  你有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要和我去玩玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,325)\fs14}doppelgänger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道「分身」一說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要是看見了  災厄將會降臨其身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  瞎說啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.53,0:01:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帥呆了  你看見他那表情了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和他說了幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後他自己就對號入座了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫針眼來著？眼皮都腫了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很快就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒是  不過很不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下個月就升到三年級了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  到時候也十五歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是不好  覺得沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如中考之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  別讓我想起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件是不是太花俏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？我倒是不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要買給我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我要穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用老是照鏡子很輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這用法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輪廓不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著有點來氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像「來辨真假」一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  你好像說過能看見什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:04:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我身上也能看到什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這雙眼  我覺得很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右眼的顏色不同感覺很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是叫異色症來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫雙色瞳啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮起來太浪費了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可愛的臉蛋就這麼白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這不是在繞著彎子說自己也可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這我不否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔  給我那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？為什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切  那隻娃娃那麼可愛的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲對可愛的認知有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個醜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那邊的象呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去更好一點的遊樂園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週媽媽因為人偶的展覽會要去東京  所以不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我得一個人看家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姨媽不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去你家玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四月天還下雪真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴真幸福  家裡有好多漂亮的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹  算不算二代血親來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血親？啊是的  二代血親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽和爸爸是一代血親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺奶奶是二代血親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兄弟姐妹應該也是二代血親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新的班級裡  那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在傳這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  新的班級怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有帥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是覺得  這個班級有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點像「被詛咒了」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被詛咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這種類似的傳言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那確實有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒帥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要給你介紹一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介紹啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  男生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說沒帥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲  你像做媒人的大媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是大媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡我還是頭一次來  好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是幸代姨媽做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽呢  希望你能原諒她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指光代姨媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是姨媽  也是你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼原諒不原諒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽現在還把鳴當做自己的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也真的很想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過因為讓別人收養你  心裡感到愧疚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有讓鳴離開自己身邊而產生的罪惡感  所以說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道她很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有埋怨過她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要說到心裡感到愧疚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霧果…媽媽也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從雙胞胎姐妹那裡奪走了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  更多的是害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心我會回到我親生母親身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也禁止我們倆見面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的想法也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不習慣的話  這個地方待久了可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去樓上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人偶是空虛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的房間就只有四疊半的空間外加一套被褥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好想有這樣一個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你也不是小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擺姐姐的架子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是雙胞胎  不分大小的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說先出世的就是姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該力氣大的才是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼理論…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姐姐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勤勞少女可是很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旁人看來就是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到蠻瘦的  放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瘦可不代表你瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥  小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢  發育了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲真是的  啥時候變成那種大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們第幾次一起洗澡來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候的就不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有兩三次吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從什麼時候開始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學五年級的時候來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  五年級的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天根婆婆一不小心說漏了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是早就有點察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說也太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…也對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嬰兒時候的照片一張也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我想不可能會丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在家裡偷偷找了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  剛出生時的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鳴你並排照的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的長得一模一樣  真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  明天去遊樂場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我們以前和媽媽三個人一起去的遊樂場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯  姨媽那次因為這事發了很大脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真不明白那個時候她為什麼那麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  就去那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴你有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  未咲你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普普通通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普普通通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  看著很老實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果是喜歡搖滾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的樂隊一樣是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有什麼契機之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記不大清了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  剛才你說勤勞少女了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在打工嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  在附近的豆腐店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零用錢很緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機話費也不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己玩的錢至少想要自己掙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  馬上就到爸爸的生日了  所以嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未咲和家人「相連」著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前來的時候還以為是個更大的遊樂場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們長大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  時光的流逝可真殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去快要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的鳴像姐姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾我來保護下未咲有何不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護什麼的太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是因為我的名字叫未咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是因為作為養女被送出去  那眼睛也不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道以為是自己的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想法真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻眼睛是因為生病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟養女什麼的都無關  不是任何人的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不管是未咲還是爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒有絲毫怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也會想為什麼只有我遭受這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我想結果還是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:16:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  如果是未咲作為養女被送出去  又失去左眼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會像現在的未咲一樣難過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以現在就挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  那邊不就是未咲的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜見山市真小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之還是得離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡大城市嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為學校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…  我想學音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音樂大學？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是減肥了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的  你比我還瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了  鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴也會跟著掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我絕不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保護未咲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到那麼不起眼的刺激項目居然會那麼口怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你聽懂了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前真害怕這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是挺喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴倒是意外的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的感覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為死定了  真盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說什麼死的  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我都沒活著的實感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遊樂場遇到那種事都沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那種擔心的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫化療吧？最近聽說白血病是能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎就算藥不起作用還有叫骨髓移植的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話從我這裡抽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生也說從鳴身上抽是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出院之後再去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來馬上就過生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴的生日也是一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要健康的未咲  如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是個難題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在鳴家裡看到的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我盡力試試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:22:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴  見崎鳴
